description: A mixed use development comprising 4000 residential units, including 27,261 sqm of extra care accommodation to provide 303 flats (Class C3) and 29,498 sqm of non-residential uses comprising 4,855 sqm retail & leisure (incorporating up to 3,100 sqm retails Class A1 - A5 and up to 2,782 sqm leisure Class D2), 5,450 sqm office (Class B1), 4884 sqm community (Class D1), 5,911 sqm hotel (Class C1) 2,785 sqm supermarket (Class A1), 3,205 GP Surgery (Class D1) and 2,408 sqm replacement primary school (Class D1) including access, car parking and open space. In addition to the matters set out above, details of the access, appearance, landscaping, layout and scale Phase 1 for 449 residential units and a multi use games area see 08/2782/R
